Requires-Dist: Django (>=3.0.0)
Requires-Dist: djangorestframework (>=3.0.0)
Requires-Dist: jsonschema (>=4.17.3)

Zippy Form is a django package which allows to create forms with dynamic fields with no code.

### Setup

Add the package name `zippy_form`  to your project’s settings.py file.

Run the below command on the terminal to create package migration files.
> python manage.py makemigrations zippy_form

Run the below command on the terminal to migrate.
> python manage.py migrate

Add the following url to your project’s url.py file:
> path('form/', include('zippy_form.urls'))
